  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No rain in many parts of the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Meteorological Department states that there will be no showers in several parts of the island today (28).",
        "Showers or thundershowers will occur in the Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in the Kandy, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts, a spokesman for the Department said.",
        "He added that strong winds of up to 50 kmph are expected at times in the western slopes of the central hills, in the northern, north central and northwestern provinces and in the Trincomalee and Hambantota districts."
      ],
